# Widget sync + minify + dist

Standalone scripts (`aftercare-text-widget.js`, `aftercare-badge-poll.js`) live at the shadow-app repo root. After any edit, from `aftercare-abt-shadow-app/`:

```bash
npm run sync-widget    # copies to public/*.js, writes root + public *.min.js (terser)
npm run build          # runs sync-widget then vite build — public assets land in dist/
```

Do not run terser by hand unless debugging; use `npm run sync-widget` so minified outputs stay aligned with source.
